'''Aubendo''' was one of the [[Twin Cities (Radnor)|Twin Cities]] of the planet [[Radnor/Legends|Radnor]], the other being [[Tacto]].

When Radnor faced a bioplague in the years leading up to the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], Aubendo was in one of the many areas affected by it. Aubendo was in the [[Isolation Sector]], divided from its sister city's [[Clear Sector]] by an [[energy gate]].

